          <a href="https://developer.android.com/studio/run/emulator" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">More information on APK Emulators</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <hr>
      <div id="history">
        <h2> History </h2>
        <Figure 
          image={[{ src: "/media/images/codinghome.webp", alt: "CodingHome Logo.", width: "50%", additionalClasses: "rounded-1" }]} 
          caption="CodingHome logo is owned by AT Products LLC. All rights reserved.">
          <Fragment slot="history-content">
            <p> CodingHome was founded on June 9th, 2021 by Alex Toucan and CodingLive as a place for coders and web developers to come together and share their knowledge and projects. Over the years, it has grown into a vibrant community with members from all around the world. <br>
              <br>
              The community focuses on various programming languages, web development frameworks, and coding best practices. Members can participate in coding challenges, collaborate on open-source projects, and attend virtual meetups and workshops. <br>
              <br>
              CodingHome has become a hub for learning and innovation, fostering a supportive environment where both beginners and experienced developers can thrive. The community continues to evolve, embracing new technologies and trends in the ever-changing landscape of coding and web development.
            </p>
        </Figure>
      </div>
